250
00:25:31,000 --> 00:25:32,541
He had been called to the front lines.

251
00:25:35,083 --> 00:25:36,291
Captain…

252
00:25:37,958 --> 00:25:39,625
I speak Russian,

253
00:25:40,708 --> 00:25:43,833
Because I am a senior captain of Kirovabad flight school.

254
00:25:45,500 --> 00:25:47,166
The plane was a Tu-2.

255
00:25:48,208 --> 00:25:49,958
This is a medium bomber aircraft.

256
00:25:50,041 --> 00:25:56,041
If they entrust that to your son, you know you can be proud of him.

257
00:26:01,041 --> 00:26:02,125
Thank You.

258
00:26:03,666 --> 00:26:05,375
Wait a moment, Captain.

259
00:26:07,541 --> 00:26:11,666
Nazarov has given me a guarantee. He will send my letters for review.

260
00:26:11,750 --> 00:26:13,541
